org.apache.ctakes.core.pipeline

Annotation Type PipeBitInfo


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Inherited
public @interface PipeBitInfo
    Annotation that should be used for Collection Readers, Annotators, and Cas Consumers (Writers). It may be useful for pipeline builder UIs and other human-pipeline interaction.
    Since:
    12/22/2016
    Version:
    %I%
    Author:
    SPF , chip-nlp
